msgid "# Add-DnsServerRecursionScope"
msgstr "# Add-DnsServerRecursionScope"

msgid "## SYNOPSIS"
msgstr "## 概要"

msgid "Adds a recursion scope on a DNS server."
msgstr "在DNS服务器上添加一个递归作用域。"

msgid "## SYNTAX"
msgstr "## 语法"

msgid "## DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "## 说明"

msgid ""
"The **Add-DnsServerRecursionScope** cmdlet adds a recursion scope on a Domain Name System (DNS) server.\n"
"Recursion scopes are unique instances of a group of settings that control recursion on a DNS server.\n"
"A recursion scope contains a list of forwarders and specifies whether recursion is enabled.\n"
"A DNS server can have many recursion scopes."
msgstr ""
"`Add-DnsServerRecursionScope` cmdlet "
"用于在域名系统（DNS）服务器上添加一个递归范围。递归范围是一组设置的具体实例，这些设置用于控制 DNS "
"服务器上的递归操作。每个递归范围都包含一组转发器的列表，并指定是否启用递归功能。一台 DNS 服务器可以拥有多个递归范围。"

msgid ""
"DNS server recursion policies allow you to choose a recursion scope for a set of queries.\n"
"If the DNS server is not authoritative for certain queries, DNS server recursion policies allow you to control how to resolve those queries.\n"
"You can specify which forwarders to use and whether to use recursion."
msgstr ""
"DNS服务器的递归策略允许您为一组查询选择相应的递归范围。如果DNS服务器对某些查询不具备权威解析能力，这些递归策略可以帮助您控制这些查询的解析方式。您可以指定使用哪些转发器，以及是否启用递归功能。"

msgid ""
"The legacy recursion setting and list of forwarders are now referred as the default recursion scope.\n"
"You cannot add or remove the default recursion scope, identified by name as dot (.)."
msgstr ""
"“legacy recursion settings”（旧版递归设置）以及“list of "
"forwarders”（转发器列表）现在被称为“default recursion "
"scope”（默认递归范围）。您无法添加或删除这个默认递归范围，它的名称标识为“.”（点号）。"

msgid "## EXAMPLES"
msgstr "## 示例"

msgid "### Example 1: Add a recursion scope"
msgstr "### 示例 1：添加递归作用域"

msgid ""
"This command adds a recursion scope to the DNS server.\n"
"This scope enables recursion and specifies two forwarders."
msgstr ""
"该命令为DNS服务器添加了一个递归作用域（recursion "
"scope）。这个作用域允许DNS服务器进行递归查询，并指定了两个转发器（forwarders）。"

msgid "## PARAMETERS"
msgstr "## 参数"

